{
  "texts": [
    "We believe this preprocessing method helps the crack detection models to distinguish undamaged samples and samples with small cracks.",
    "Through empirical study, we can illustrate the efficiency of the preprocessing method.",
    "In this work, the proposed models follow the encoder-decoder architecture 13, 14.",
    "Different backbone networks were tested for the encoder.",
    "Upsampling layers for the decoder were tested as well."
  ]
}